{NORTH has 22 points and opens 2\C.

SOUTH is pretty weak, right? She responds 2\D.

NORTH bids his suit, 2\H.

SOUTH is so weak she bids the second negative - 3\C.

NORTH rebids his suit, 3\H, and SOUTH passes.}

